{"title":"Why I Am Called \"MeowWow520\"","uid":"b7da3ce5f16bcbd24b24314a2bb68e5e","slug":"name","date":"2025-01-03T05:00:00.000Z","updated":"2025-01-03T03:46:04.023Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/name.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://www.helloimg.com/i/2025/01/03/67773f4eb4d06.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"前言\"><a href=\"#前言\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"前言\"></a>前言</h1><p>这个名字的由来，耐人寻味。如果你好奇的话，就此读下去吧！</p>\n<h1 id=\"MeowWow520\"><a href=\"#MeowWow520\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"MeowWow520\"></a>MeowWow520</h1><h2 id=\"那一年我，有了QQ\"><a href=\"#那一年我，有了QQ\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"那一年我，有了QQ\"></a>那一年我，有了QQ</h2><p>对电子设备的渴望，大多数来自于对社交媒体的渴望。<br>大概在2018年，在家人的支持下，我打开了QQ的注册界面。<br>头像，昵称，签名……这些现在我信手沾来的东西，对于那时的我可不是very friendly<br>不知是，大脑的短路，还是小脑的萎缩。<strong>Hello</strong> 成为了我的第一个网名。由此以后的众多网名，都在他的基础上演变<br>———— <strong>hello-bye</strong> ect.</p>\n<h2 id=\"我爱“喵喵”\"><a href=\"#我爱“喵喵”\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"我爱“喵喵”\"></a>我爱“喵喵”</h2><p>每一位铲屎官的脑海中，时时刻刻都有cats的叫声。对喵咪的喜爱，促使我开始更改我的name。<br>于是，最初的原型，梦开始的地方，出现了。<br>“ <strong>喵喵</strong> ”，用拟声词做昵称。现在我想想<del>就觉得我太愚蠢了。</del></p>\n<h2 id=\"一切的开始\"><a href=\"#一切的开始\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"一切的开始\"></a>一切的开始</h2><p>电子爱好者（X）电子游戏爱好者（V）<br>我对电脑游戏，开始于一个经典的作品————<a href=\"www.minecraft.net\">Minecraft</a>。冈易版不必多说，中文名随随便便。<br>但当我来到国际版，哪怕是离线国际版。everything is gone。<br>我必须使用一个<del>纯</del>英文的昵称了，虽然中文的昵称我纠结了很久，但是英文的并没有。我打开翻译软件，直接翻译“喵喵”得到了“meowmeow”这个结果。<br>用这个？明显我觉得太奇怪了this name。<br><strong>awa</strong> 什么意思？我不知道，但我当时很喜欢把他当emmm使用，而且看着也很可爱。so it was created ———— <strong>Meowawa</strong> 。</p>\n<h2 id=\"我又做出了改变\"><a href=\"#我又做出了改变\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"我又做出了改变\"></a>我又做出了改变</h2><p>在离线<a href=\"www.minecraft.net\">Minecraft</a>中，我可以起任意的英文名。我可以体验 <strong>dream</strong> 的名字打但也仅仅只是体验<br>在2021年假，我得到了人生的第一台电脑，他陪伴我至今（2025年）。</p>\n","feature":true,"text":"这个奇怪的名字背后藏着什么？...","permalink":"/post/name","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":691,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"About Me","slug":"About-Me","count":3,"path":"api/tags/About-Me.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80\"><span class=\"toc-text\">前言</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#MeowWow520\"><span class=\"toc-text\">MeowWow520</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%82%A3%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E6%88%91%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%86QQ\"><span class=\"toc-text\">那一年我，有了QQ</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%88%91%E7%88%B1%E2%80%9C%E5%96%B5%E5%96%B5%E2%80%9D\"><span class=\"toc-text\">我爱“喵喵”</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%80%E5%88%87%E7%9A%84%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">一切的开始</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%88%91%E5%8F%88%E5%81%9A%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%86%E6%94%B9%E5%8F%98\"><span class=\"toc-text\">我又做出了改变</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"MeowWow520","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://www.helloimg.com/i/2024/12/06/6752895137ed9.jpg","link":"meowwow520.cn","description":"I am MeowWow520,Welcome To Here.There will be my part of life.","socials":{}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{"title":"Hello World！","uid":"2e60799cec5dfad09dbbeafeecf46a1f","slug":"Hello_world","date":"2025-01-03T07:00:00.000Z","updated":"2025-01-03T03:52:36.021Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Hello_world.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://www.helloimg.com/i/2025/01/03/67775e4343f03.jpg","text":"你好啊！欢迎来到我的Blog。...","permalink":"/post/Hello_world","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":6,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"About Me","slug":"About-Me","count":3,"path":"api/tags/About-Me.json"}],"author":{"name":"MeowWow520","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://www.helloimg.com/i/2024/12/06/6752895137ed9.jpg","link":"meowwow520.cn","desc